Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I made contact with him last night, \Nbut he ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.82,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Bugbear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.45,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,His combat abilities rival, or exceed, my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.83,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Even before he awakens, there could \Nbe trouble if you aren't careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:22.04,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we don't currently know \Nwhat singularity he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:26.50,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then getting into the ring was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:30.59,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like so much fun, \NI couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:35.61,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we went through all the trouble \Nto bring the Bakuretsujuu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:37.68,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.62,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If we lure him out, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.91,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Magus{\i0} incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.46,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Was this a year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:48.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.26,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that it never hit the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:58.41,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I kill a guy with my singularity last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:07.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay, Haruhiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vice Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Late last night, was there an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.44,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't received any information about one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:52.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A strange vibration shook the arena last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,just as the lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:03:00.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean it was this \Ndesigner child's singularity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:01.67,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,According to our investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:06.95,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,that arena has a number of \Nillegally collected boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:12.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,How powerful is a Planetary Gear's singularity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you have a singularity, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Before your first launch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:23.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,weren't you able to sense how \Nterrifying the Kiltgang are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a type of singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.18,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Livlaster's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.39,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you call your Livlaster "DC," Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:38.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't short for designer child, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"DC" stands for "Dream Catcher."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Dream Catcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Like the talisman that keeps nightmares away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to it, I've stopped having bad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:59.13,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.59,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, every night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:07.67,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,But I have nightmares when I'm awake, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:12.02,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Having Haruhiko as my fiancé is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.40,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,It was your father's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:21.07,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,My father sees people only as tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.86,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the biggest nightmare is the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.66,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,that my father is buying and selling children!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.08,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.15,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any right to say this, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.42,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.21,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,the one who bought you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.43,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I did the same thing as my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:51.06,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.39,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me a place to belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.11,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Baku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.23,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,This city is where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.63,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Baku, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.26,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Will you show me that trick again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.43,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,This was my only picture of my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.90,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,My father found it, and tore it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.37,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Baku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:04.99,Default - flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.51,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.91,Default - flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,A magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.15,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Please... You can do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:41.22,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you be able to use that trick
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:45.17,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,to restore the ace of hearts alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:51.76,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't have that level of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:59.14,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that isn't really a magic trick at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:02.40,Title,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1739,1)\an9}My Town
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:18.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hitting a stationary target is nothing to brag about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.08,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.63,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It seems even that's difficult for the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:25.53,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:28.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've never practiced shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing pretty well in real fights, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.21,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.68,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Would you try it with the Livlaster next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.36,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, no matter how often I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.87,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,The Science Chief says it isn't \Nthat you're firing the Livlaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:00.45,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,but that it's using you to fire itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.84,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:08.17,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel like the Livlaster \Nis controlling me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It feels more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Natural, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.09,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:23.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't look at your right hand \Nand think, "This is my right hand," do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your right hand's a part of you, \Nso it's natural for it to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like it's me and the Livlaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's like both of us comprise "me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I fire the Livlaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:38.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,it feels more like throwing a boomerang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,than shooting a handgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.95,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly is a singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.54,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:50.59,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.36,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.02,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,That was Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.76,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hana had another premonition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.33,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, a Machine Goodfellow will activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:02.64,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That arena seems like the first place to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.27,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:07.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the Nebula Engine at Haneda, \Naboard the Regenbogen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:13.38,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,For strategic reasons, we're \Npreparing it to be sent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.15,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we'll have to rely on the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.45,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.98,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go one-on-one again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:25.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:28.71,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... H-Hello, Kariya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.67,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Business seems to be booming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.19,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thanks to Baku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.55,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,He's our cash cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.17,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.18,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, have him earn as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:41.81,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:45.98,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This will be our last time seeing him in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, have someone replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.36,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Does... that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:55.82,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:59.08,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'll do as you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.78,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Teppei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.75,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to run to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.81,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom, bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:32.89,Default,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:39.45,Default,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,This corridor is off-limits to unauthorized persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was looking for the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:48.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're the champion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.92,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:57.42,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you afraid of fights with no rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.13,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:07.23,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of not being able to \Nprotect what's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.24,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,And there's the gong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:26.16,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Our undefeated emperor, Baku, \Nfaces off against Great Ramdes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.54,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A fierce battle has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Amarok and Moco aren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.08,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:37.29,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,Great Ramdes has started by \Nbringing out wooden swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.09,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,But non-ranged weapons are not against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:49.53,Default,MC,0000,0000,0000,,He grabbed the swords in mid-swing, \Nwith his bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,His strength is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it really is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.85,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He seems different, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The strength to want to protect something, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:29.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you want to say, Baku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.89,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I have one thing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.56,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This is my town!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That was Miss Kumiko's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:44.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.11,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.07,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.23,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.19,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:21.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Agree to our terms, and we'll release her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.34,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.15,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.95,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.28,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.63,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Baku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.69,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Bugbear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:46.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's continue what we started last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:53.02,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you've been up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.05,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.62,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:36.27,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.39,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.91,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I was shot, but I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.80,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds are nearly gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.18,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.04,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:08.46,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I always wondered about that \Nstrange magic trick of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.18,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the {\i1}Magus{\i0} incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.98,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,When a ship was blown up in Yokohama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,An Asanoda ship was blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:31.59,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the Asanoda were aboard \Nthe ship when it exploded,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,but no one died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.13,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.66,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's feelings activated a singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:52.88,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the depths of despair at \Nthe world that surrounded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.98,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,At least go out and say hello, Kumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:07.66,Default - flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, isn't that a bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.61,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:11.05,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,It was in our basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.02,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.03,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, everyone's aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:20.37,Default - flashback,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I can put an end to your child trafficking with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.71,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:45.15,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,The dream I have each night is true, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:50.14,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reason I'm alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:56.04,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay now, Baku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:01.32,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.83,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Baku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:08.04,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Release me from this nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.14,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trick was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:20.52,Default,Mo,0000,0000,0000,,When the {\i1}Magus{\i0} exploded,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:24.27,Default,Mo,0000,0000,0000,,everyone in the Asanoda Yakuza actually died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:30.53,Default,Mo,0000,0000,0000,,To revive her, Baku brought back \Neveryone else who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.49,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are a special person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:40.07,Default,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Live in a way that lets you see the true light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:51.75,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,They're like an illusion Bugbear created.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:57.33,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,You can't bring back the dead with a singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They die because they aren't completely human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.97,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You remember now... Right, Bugbear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.94,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:09.97,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:12.07,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,This planet is a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.57,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.53,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Goodfellow Bakuretsujuu, activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.74,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Abreaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.54,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,MM bus signal detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.88,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Identifying epicenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.33,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Initiating launch sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.59,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:15.67,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.34,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine Ordinary, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:39.28,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the face-off between the \NBakuretsujuu and the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Earth Engine's starting \Noff with a deadly weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But ranged weapons are against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Bugbear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's overwhelming the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:14.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The way he's fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:18.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:40.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep running, you'll run \Nout of time, Daichi Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.89,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.32,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,He's very fierce, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.41,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.95,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel any strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:14.46,Default - italics,B,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing left to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.57,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:49.68,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I broke it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.49,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:55.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who the designer \Nchild on board was?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.08,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:04.30,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That strong person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.77,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He was tough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:09.26,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It almost felt like he wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:18.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Bugbear?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.57,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:31.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:34.16,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:35.98,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,My town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:42.42,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,My town, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:19.16,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,A premonition says there won't be any \NMachine Goodfellows for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:21.60,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,so at Akari's suggestion, we take a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:28.40,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,But the Planetary Gears attack Tanegashima \Nin a way none of us expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:32.07,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 14 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:34.70,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,A Maiden's Tear That Sparkled Through the Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:34.70,Title2,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,A Maiden's Tear That Sparkled Through the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.16,0:24:37.58,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, scramble!
